skinparam packageStyle rectangle

legend bottom
  |<PATTERN_COLOR> Pattern | Design Pattern |
  |<MODEL_COLOR> Model | Domain Model |
  |<FACTORY_COLOR> Factory | Factory Pattern |
  |<OBSERVER_COLOR> Observer | Observer Pattern |
  |<EVENT_COLOR> Event | Event/Data Type |
