' ===========================================
' RELATIONSHIPS BETWEEN PACKAGES
' ===========================================

' Strategy Pattern relationships
EvaluationStrategy ..> Exam : evaluates
EvaluationStrategy ..> Question : uses
EvaluationStrategy ..> Response : evaluates

' Decorator Pattern relationships
ExamDecorator ..> Exam : decorates
ExamDecoratorFactory ..> Attempt : enhances results

' Builder Pattern relationships
SyllabusBuilder ..> Syllabus : builds

' Composite Pattern relationships
EducationalComponent ..> EducationLevel : represents
EducationalComponent ..> Field : represents
EducationalComponent ..> Subject : represents
EducationalComponent ..> LearningUnit : represents

' Observer Pattern relationships
EventPublisher ..> Event : publishes
IObserver ..> Event : receives
EmailNotificationObserver ..> User : notifies
XPUpdateObserver ..> LearnerProfile : updates
NotificationObserver ..> Notification : creates

' Authentication Strategy relationships
IAuthStrategy ..> User : creates/updates
CredentialsAuthStrategy ..> User : authenticates
GoogleAuthStrategy ..> User : authenticates
GitHubAuthStrategy ..> User : authenticates
AuthStrategyManager ..> User : manages

' Factory relationships
ProfileFactory ..> EventPublisher : publishes events
ProfileFactoryV2 ..> User : uses

note top of ProfileFactory
  Factory Method Pattern
  (src/lib/factories/)
  Creates users and their
  associated profiles in transaction
end note

note top of ProfileFactoryV2
  Factory Method Pattern
  (src/lib/profile-factory.ts)
  Creates or retrieves profiles
  for existing users
end note

note top of EvaluationStrategyFactory
  Factory Pattern
  Creates appropriate evaluation
  strategy based on exam type
end note

note top of AuthStrategyManager
  Singleton + Strategy Pattern
  Manages authentication providers
  Easily extensible for new OAuth providers
end note

note top of EventPublisher
  Singleton + Observer Pattern
  Central event management
end note

note top of SyllabusBuilder
  Builder Pattern
  Constructs complex
  syllabus structures
end note

note top of EducationalComponent
  Composite Pattern
  Represents hierarchical
  educational structure
end note

note top of ExamDecorator
  Decorator Pattern
  Adds dynamic features
  to exam evaluation
end note

note top of EvaluationStrategy
  Strategy Pattern
  Different evaluation algorithms
  for different exam types
end note

note top of IAuthStrategy
  Strategy Pattern
  Supports multiple authentication
  providers (Credentials, Google, GitHub)
  Easy to extend with new providers
end note

@enduml
